des: Created by a licensed Speech Language Pathologist. This skill allows users to practice with their speech generating devices. This skill is not marketed to (or for sole use by) children, and is to be used only with direct adult supervision (included by not limited to parental, teacher, medical professionals) to assist with speech device practice. We do not store information about users of this skill.
